snippet.title: Super Skull Smash Go! Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for the upcoming retro spectacular SUPER SKULL SMASH GO!  from TACS games (http://tacsgames.com).

Journey through 4 worlds smashing skulls and ridding the haunted towns of their skeletons and zombies. Puzzle platforming action like you've seen before!

Looks like an 8-bit game, plays like a 16-bit game!
Authentic 8-bit soundtrack recorded from DMG-01!
4 world to complete!
27 levels in total!
puzzle platforming action like never seen before!

Get your retro fix soon!
